EmailTemplate.name: Senior College Tour & IB Invite
EmailTemplate.subject: Invitation to Senior College Events: Make your final school years count!
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Lead.FirstName}
I'm delighted to invite you along to the following Senior College events:
Senior College Tour on Tuesday 12 June 9.00am: Meet our Head of School and Head of Senior College, tour our unique facilities and learning spaces, and chat with current students to discover the benefits of joining our city learning community. You will gain a great insight into student life in the city and the numerous opportunities on offer at St Andrew’s. Our Senior College campus offers a dynamic, coeducational learning environment in the heart of the city for students in Years 10-12.
IB Information Evening on Tuesday 19 June at 5.30pm
Offering students a broad range of learning skills and subject areas, the IB Diploma Programme provides a truly international curriculum that is taught in 150 countries worldwide. Come along and find out everything you need to know about the IB, including:
Who chooses to study the IB; Subject choices and what students learn; How IB assessment works; and How to be a successful IB learner and what it means to part of a global community of learners.
Our current IB students, teachers and IB graduates will also share their IB experiences.
Bookings are essential. Please book your place via our website at https://www.sacs.nsw.edu.au/book-a-tour/tour-bookings/.
I look forward to welcoming you to our Senior College.
Regards
Bruce Perry
Registrar/Mathematics Teacher
Sydney Square, Sydney NSW 2000, Australia direct +61 2 9286 9507 mobile email bperry@sacs.nsw.edu.au phone +61 2 9286 9500 fax +61 2 9286 9550
www.sacs.nsw.edu.au
St Andrew's Cathedral School is an Anglican day school for boys and girls from Kindergarten to Year 12 located in the heart of Sydney.
You are receiving this invitation as you have previously indicated interest in enrolment at St Andrew’s Cathedral School. We would love you to come to along on our Senior College Tour however, if you would like to unsubscribe from further invitations, please click here.
